#: ../../U/UBD.rst:9
msgid ""
"[abbreviation for ‘User Brain Damage’] An abbreviation used to close out "
"trouble reports obviously due to utter cluelessness on the user's part. "
"Compare :ref:`pilot-error`\\, :ref:`PEBKAC`\\, :ref:`idiot`\\; oppose "
":ref:`PBD`\\; see also :ref:`brain-damaged`\\."
msgstr ""
"[‘User Brain Damage’(ユーザの脳の損傷)の略] 明らかにユーザ側の完全な無知に起因するトラブル報告を片付けるために使われる略語。\\"
" :ref:`pilot-error`\\ 、\\ :ref:`PEBKAC`\\ 、\\ :ref:`idiot`\\ と比較し、\\ "
":ref:`PBD`\\ と対比せよ。\\ :ref:`brain-damaged`\\ も参照。"
